data.description: Motivated seller huge price reduction for a quick sale!  Corner Lot All-Brick Ranch: Perfect for First-Time Homebuyers & Investors with Rate Buy Down Advantage    Attention first-time homebuyers and astute investors: Your next opportunity is here! Introducing a classic three-bedroom, one and a half bath all-brick ranch, strategically situated on a prime corner lot in a serene locale.    Step into spaces bursting with potential. The expansive living areas eagerly await your vision, while the character-filled kitchen stands on the brink of a modern-day makeover. Sun-drenched bedrooms ensure restful nights, with the master suite adding a touch of luxury with its private bath.    Beyond its walls, the vast fenced backyard unfurls, offering limitless possibilities. Whether it's a vibrant garden, a child's wonderland, or a tranquil retreat, this canvas is yours to paint.    The standout feature? A $4,500 rate buy down available for qualifying buyers, making this both a smart start for first-time homeowners and a lucrative pick for investors. With its compelling financial incentives and undeniable potential, this corner lot ranch is a golden ticket to a prosperous property future. Don't let this gem slip through your grasp!  Home Newley renovated in 2016 and offers fiber.
